"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"I’m writing this to expose this American government for war crimes. Specifically, crimes against humanity (against myself). \\n\\nI am being gaslighted and harassed daily by this Nazi American government and I have no idea why. \\n\\nHow?\\n\\n\\n---\\n\\nThey are pretty **blatant** in harassing me daily actually. For instance, I worked night shift stocking at a City Market supermarket for one year. And almost daily they would send cops inside of the store to shop around. \\\\[Here\\\\](\\n\\n[https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmXRpUAWfc6dkDGUVaKhWgStFPkYJPwR2jwbsGptTv6YMo/](https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmXRpUAWfc6dkDGUVaKhWgStFPkYJPwR2jwbsGptTv6YMo/)\\n\\n) is proof. \\n\\nThey also find it comical to send cops to the grocery store at the same time that I’m going to buy groceries. \\n\\nThis is obvious evidence that they **spy on me** through my cell phone. Proof that what Edward Snowden and other whistleblowers have exposed is truth. \\n\\n\\n---\\n\\nI also worked at a fast food restaurant and the same thing would occur. Cops would drive past the drive thru window almost daily. \\n\\nThis was now 2 years of harassment at my jobs.\\n\\n I should mention that he supermarket job would get audited continually. And the drive thru job that I had would have 1 - 3 health inspections per month. Causing me to get home at 2am sometimes just to clean the store thoroughly. I’m sure they found this hilarious.\\n\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Road harassment/gaslighting by cops\\n\\nI would leave the drive thru job at 12am midnight and drive home. They had a **sheriff** park on the highway **for an entire week in the same spot** at midnight and on the 6th or 7th day of this he stopped me. Why? For going 5mph over the speed limit. \\n\\nThe reason for the “speeding” (5mph over) was because I switched to the left lane (I was in the slow lane and he was on the shoulder) and hit the gas a little. \\n\\n\\n---\\n\\nThese Nazis always have sheriffs/cops on the road whenever I go out for anything. Sometimes when I’m carpooling they have a cop drive in front of the car I’m in, for about 10 - 15 miles, doing nothing but causing traffic. \\n\\n\\n---\\n\\n## They drive sirens by my home daily\\n\\nThe Nazis have cops, ambulances, and fire trucks drive sirens by my home daily for 2 years. Again more propaganda/gaslighting to induce paranoia in myself for whatever their narcissistic/psychopathic reasons are. \\n\\nNot to mention that they drive cops by me anytime I walk to my job or go out anywhere. \\n\\nHow do I know they are targeting me using psyops? \\n\\n* They send cops to shop at grocery stores at the same time that I arrive (almost every time I grocery shop). \\n\\n\\n* They had a cop in Aspen, CO go into a pizza shop as I was leaving with my pizza\\n* Sending cops to my jobs daily to intimidate and harass me.\\n* About three years ago a I read a tweet and it changed suddenly to the words “cops monitoring” after refreshing the page.\\n\\nThere is much more deception and gaslighting that I don’t care to mention a the moment. \\n\\nThis American government is the definition of tyrants. \\n\\nI don’t fear you. ;)\",\"timestamp\":1642641463,\"title\":\"I've been harassed DAILY for 3 years now at my job, home, and life by COPS in Colorado. \"},\"digest\":\"rFtXdE-X0MwFYO56tRsWkcAtdZHMC7yBjAU2IQvzkc0\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xD9658151adb9551171770f70fc99d74D73c5bb2A\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Oba5I5VatJ5jC1-mpYCo_3DIwYRXWw7108CnOf_Mef8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Hk-yTbeSGjQA7uWzaXy_uFBoXUEY88gf9boIcbAArV0\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"VSGD-P8MQz23PQpxOwShBeNU36vNbFYxF-IpoKcznhtiyevAmmLbMTcAXdLxkg5vF81W1WsnyISdMDg6L6VSzA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x2ec858f0dc2058c96b5d0b8fbb66bbbcc2599ee244a76843155783c8888bde1a740d52bb29961d126b14b7352e6f537eeee2984c6d68d4a5ef713a017ba6cefc1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this devic